{"tid":362703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"M記想做死我地一班新移民？","createTime":"2017-08-17T06:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T08:42:33.000Z","uid":1734,"like":8,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76e7e0a47fc7f1915b3bc6cc0e5e216fef4ff65b","tid":362703,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"我係潮州人，係大陸我中西餐都識煮，後尾結婚黎左香港。<br />\n<br />\n搵左好耐工都無人請，笑我廣東話都未講正 ！<br />\n<br />\n後尾經熟人介紹入跨國企業做大廚，話好有發揮空間 <br />\n<br />\n點知係麥當勞，不過唔緊要啦，我相信我地潮州佬終有出頭天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做左幾年終於升左做紅牌，人工都大幅上升 ，老婆都好開心 。<br />\n<br />\n但呢排日日搞優惠 我前日炸雞炸到手軟，琴日又要整批 <br />\n<br />\n今日做豬強做到死，真係好辛苦，有冇人明白新移民痛苦！"},{"pid":"5e80e556ec322afee5f4c7c57e0d756a41ca5db5","tid":362703,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"樓主南亞人"},{"pid":"2423a5439c2bd6c7b1179f690a3dc0d8e309bb2c","tid":362703,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"死返大陸啦"},{"pid":"3a572e133c919ed514abb450721697caa5aea1ad","tid":362703,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死返大陸啦</blockquote><br />\n我係香港未有出頭 我唔會走 潮州人唔衰得"},{"pid":"a7c4616798bda661a68c68cc85026f5f45f96be5","tid":362703,"uid":23170,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"幾好，McDonald's依啲高級西餐廳都俾你入到"},{"pid":"b9826685ed3a6abdec69ae704314744e20ce6739","tid":362703,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主南亞人</blockquote><br />\n潮州人"},{"pid":"6b0cfffdec2cdc4fe681c44bf131b90dcc7b7203","tid":362703,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死返大陸啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f4a80f991fe12ef3d6163445698e8e77604dfd70","tid":362703,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"53d004a5bd62